cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on image-based camera localization, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new framework that combines a generative model with the Kalman filter, which involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.RO, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
